## 子组件 B：五层记忆系统（3d）

**修改** `packages/core/src/state/memory-db.ts` 大幅扩展

### 架构概述

来自分析文档十二.组件21。五层记忆结构：

| 层 | 名称 | 内容 | 存储方式 | 访问频率 |
|:--:|------|------|----------|:--------:|
| T0 | 不可变规则 | book_rules, style_guide, genre_pact | JSON 文件 | 每章读取 |
| T1 | 当前状态 | 角色状态、位置、关系 | snapshots/state.json | 每章读+写 |
| T2 | 活跃叙事 | 弧线进度、伏笔到期提醒 | memory-db 表 | 每章读+写 |
| T3 | 层级摘要 | 章节摘要、卷摘要、全书摘要 | memory-db 表 + 文件 | 规划时读取 |
| T4 | 原始档案 | 完整章节内容 | chapters/目录 | 审计时读取 |

### Step 1：T2 活跃叙事表（1d）

```typescript
// memory-db.ts 新增

export interface ActiveNarrative {
  readonly id: string;
  readonly type: "arc" | "hook" | "subplot";
  readonly status: "active" | "paused" | "completed" | "abandoned";
  readonly lastUpdatedChapter: number;
  readonly nextDueChapter?: number;    // 伏笔到期提醒
  readonly summary: string;
  readonly relatedCharacterIds: string[];
}

// 新增方法
db.addActiveNarrative(narrative: ActiveNarrative): Promise<void>;
db.getActiveNarratives(chapterNumber: number): Promise<ActiveNarrative[]>;
db.getDueHooks(chapterNumber: number): Promise<ActiveNarrative[]>;
db.updateNarrativeStatus(id: string, status: string): Promise<void>;
```

### Step 2：T3 层级摘要增量更新（1d）

```typescript
export interface ChapterSummary {
  readonly chapterNumber: number;
  readonly summary: string;
  readonly keyEvents: string[];
  readonly characterStates: Record<string, string>;
  readonly emotionalArc: string;
  readonly hookChanges: string[];
}

export interface VolumeSummary {
  readonly volumeNumber: number;
  readonly chapters: [number, number];  // 起止章号
  readonly summary: string;
  readonly majorArcProgress: string[];
  readonly remainingHooks: string[];
}

// 增量更新逻辑：新章加入后只更新受影响的摘要节点
export async function incrementallyUpdateSummaries(
  bookDir: string,
  newChapterSummary: ChapterSummary,
): Promise<void> {
  // 1. 更新该章摘要
  // 2. 如果该章是卷的结尾，更新卷摘要
  // 3. 如果卷是全书的关键节点，更新全书摘要
  // 4. 只更新变化的部分，不重新生成全部
}
```

### Step 3：Agent 检索策略配置（0.5d）

```typescript
// 各 Agent 的检索配置
export const AGENT_MEMORY_ACCESS: Record<string, {
  readonly read: ReadonlyArray<"T0" | "T1" | "T2" | "T3" | "T4">;
  readonly write: ReadonlyArray<"T0" | "T1" | "T2" | "T3" | "T4">;
}> = {
  director:  { read: ["T0", "T2"], write: ["T2"] },
  planner:   { read: ["T1", "T3"], write: [] },
  writer:    { read: ["T1", "T2"], write: [] },
  continuity: { read: ["T1", "T2", "T4"], write: [] },
  observer:  { read: [], write: ["T1", "T2", "T3"] },
};
```

### Step 4：混合检索评分（0.5d）

```typescript
export function rankMemoryResults(
  lexical: Array<{ id: string; score: number }>,
  semantic: Array<{ id: string; score: number }>,
  recency: Array<{ id: string; chapterNumber: number }>,
  hookDue: Array<{ id: string; nextDueChapter: number }>,
  currentChapter: number,
): Array<{ id: string; finalScore: number }> {
  // 加权公式:
  // finalScore = 0.3 * lexical + 0.3 * semantic
  //             + 0.2 * recency + 0.2 * hookDue
  // 其中 recency = 1 - (currentChapter - chapterNumber) / maxGap
  // 其中 hookDue = nextDueChapter 越近越高
}
```

**完成标准**：
- [ ] T2 活跃叙事表就绪，伏笔到期可查询
- [ ] T3 层级摘要增量更新不重复生成
- [ ] Agent 检索策略配置生效
- [ ] 混合检索评分可用

## Phase 3.5 完成标准

